title: PJ Harvey Live In Concert From San Francisco's Warfield Theater
description: Iconoclastic singer-songwriter PJ Harvey is making four U.S. stops in support of her recent album Let England Shake. Hear one of those concerts featuring songs from her latest album 'Let England Shake,' recorded live from the Warfield Theater in San Francisco on April 14, 2011. To hear the full concert, visit our website, npr.org/music. Set List: 1) "Let England Shake" 2) "The Words That Maketh Murder" 3) "All & Everyone" 4) "In the Dark Places" 5) "The Glorious Land" 6) "The Last Living Rose" 7)"England" 8) "Bitter Branches" 9) "On Battleship Hill" 10) "The Colour of the Earth"
